&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;PART-TIME RECEPTIONIST/ADMINISTRATOR REQUIRED &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;25 HOURS MON - FRIDAY&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Due to expansion Nantgarw Road Medical Centre is looking for a receptionist/administrator to work with our committed and friendly team, to start as soon as possible. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Candidates must be computer literate and have a good telephone manner. Previous experience in a surgery environment and experience of EMISweb or Vision computer system a distinct advantage. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duties include answering the telephone, booking appointments, patient follow up for test results, coordination of requests for medical reports, stationery ordering, processing of incoming correspondence. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Successful applicants are required to provide a standard disclosure barring service check. Employer will meet disclosure expense.to 30 hours , &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;plus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;additional paid hours depending on the needs of surgery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
